        <hr noshade size="1">
        
        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">Everything you'd want to know about tinkering is at the Tinkering Compendium:  <a href="http://www.eqportal.com/tinkering/" target="_blank">http://www.eqportal.com/tinkering/</a></P><P>With 5 charges, maybe it becomes more of an emergency survival kit than a standard tactic.  But there's nothing wrong with having an emergency survival kit at 18 pp...</P><P>Also, if you're skilling up Tinkering, it's cheaper to get past 75 making Stalking Probes instead of Spyglasses.</P><P><b>Morty Undercrypt</b>, Keeper of the <font color=red>NecroGnomicon</font id=red><BR><small>"Whoops, was I supposed to be taking names too?"</small><BR>E'ci<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
